{"id":294898,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/维权网-各地维权访民强烈要求释放被刑事拘留的/","date":"2013-05-23T22:31:17Z","modified":"2013-05-23T22:31:17Z","title":"维权网 | 各地维权访民强烈要求释放被刑事拘留的邓志波等人（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员孙雨报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>，邓志波、赵广军、吕动力、张继新、王素娥被北京西城分局刑事拘留后。各地维权访民感到极为震惊和愤慨，同时更加担忧身患肝病等多种疾病的邓志波的身体健康状况。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日</span><span>，在京都维权访民打出《抗议非法拘捕，要求释放邓志波、赵广军、吕动力、张继新、王素娥》的横幅，再次举行声援活动。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>大家一致认为正常的维权没有违法，中国加入世贸组织和世界接轨，而世界诸多国家的官员都自觉公开财产，我们要求官员公开财产也没有错。希望当局依法公正的解决当事人的诉求，纠正冤假错案，不要用打压的办法激化矛盾。上访多年诉求不解决反而遭受打压的现状不应再继续，政府应该遵守宪法，依法保障公民的信访权、人身自由权、健康权等各项基本权利。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>参与抗议声援的人士有：黑龙江陈秀娟、杜春艳，吉林赵云侠、杨忠和，上海项文寅、吴玉芬，天津郑建慧等人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-8QU2Vv_odKI/UZ42pJmS2-I/AAAAAAAAifc/9iTnjzUekIo/s1600/22.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"212\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-8QU2Vv_odKI/UZ42pJmS2-I/AAAAAAAAifc/9iTnjzUekIo/s320/22.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-XSk6RtbXdlI/UZ42tcuKOMI/AAAAAAAAifk/GgdQmwnBhWk/s1600/118.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"203\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-XSk6RtbXdlI/UZ42tcuKOMI/AAAAAAAAifk/GgdQmwnBhWk/s1600/118.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-K8s7P635LO4/UZ42xY0tmvI/AAAAAAAAifs/WJi_qiKf0Cc/s1600/131.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-K8s7P635LO4/UZ42xY0tmvI/AAAAAAAAifs/WJi_qiKf0Cc/s320/131.JPG\" width=\"241\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></spa